---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import SocialIcons from './SocialIcons.astro'


const {fullName, title, institute, MyPicture} = Astro.props
---
<div class='flex-1'>
  <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold mb-4'>
    <p>Welcome to my website</p>
    <p>This is <span class='text-secondary'>{fullName}</span></p>
  </h1>
  <p class='text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4'>{title}{institute ? ` at ${institute}` : ''}</p>
<p class="text-lg mb-6 first-letter:text-5xl first-letter:font-bold first-letter:text-accent first-letter:float-left first-letter:mr-1 first-letter:leading-none">
  Yang Chia-Yu 是一名研究超基性與蛇紋岩土壤的博士後研究員，
  透過<strong>礦物學、磁化率與地球化學（Cr–Ni–Fe 系統）</strong>探討母岩與氣候對成土作用的影響。
</p>
<p class="text-lg mb-6">
  同時，她也研究以岩石促進風化（ERW）達成碳移除與永續農業的可能性。
</p>
<p class="text-lg mb-6">
   她的<strong>目標</strong>是建立一個連結土壤演化、礦物轉化與全球環境變遷的整合框架。
</p>
  <p class='text-base mb-6'></p>    
    Dr. Chia-Yu Yang is a postdoctoral researcher in soil science focusing on ultramafic and serpentine soils. 
    Her work integrates soil mineralogy, magnetic susceptibility, and geochemistry (Cr–Ni–Fe systems) to understand how parent material and climate shape pedogenesis. 
    She also explores enhanced rock weathering (ERW) as a pathway for carbon removal and sustainable agriculture. 
    Her goal is to build a unified framework linking soil evolution, mineral transformation, and global environmental change.
  </p>
  <div class='flex gap-4'>
    <SocialIcons />
  </div>
</div>
<div class="size-72 lg:block hidden">
  <Image
    src={MyPicture}
    alt={fullName}
    class="w-full h-full object-cover mask mask-circle"
  />
</div>